TITLE: Implementing Safe Stream Resolvers with Repeater in GraphQL Yoga
DESCRIPTION: Creates a GraphQL Yoga server with a safe streaming implementation using Repeater instead of AsyncGenerators to prevent memory leaks when streams are canceled.
SOURCE: https://github.com/graphql-hive/graphql-yoga/blob/main/website/src/content/docs/features/defer-stream.mdx#2025-04-15_snippet_6

