TITLE: Background Jobs Management Plugin in GraphQL Yoga
DESCRIPTION: Plugin implementation for managing background jobs queue, adding analytics jobs during request parsing and flushing the queue on server disposal
SOURCE: https://github.com/graphql-hive/graphql-yoga/blob/main/website/src/content/docs/features/envelop-plugins.mdx#2025-04-15_snippet_6

